snippet.title: Paths: Beatrice's Adventure - Official Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Play Store:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ThreeLeaves.PathsBeatriceAdventure

iOS:
https://apps.apple.com/us/app/paths-beatrices-adventure/id1622536094

Paths: Beatrice's Adventure is an upcoming story-driven game with more than 10 endings. It is developed by Three Leaves Studio and it is published by FredBear Games in collaboration with PlayPlayFun.

Official Page:
https://playplayfun.com/paths-beatrices-adventure/

Facebook Page:
https://www.facebook.com/pathbeatriceadventuregame

Credits:
Music: www.bensound.com
